{"tid":2063201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：未有證據顯示祿泉樓出現空氣傳播","createTime":"2020-06-13T17:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:52:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1afc568d54fce33f8397338471669d95beb2fb8","tid":2063201,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：未有證據顯示祿泉樓出現空氣傳播<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】祿泉樓最新確診的男患者，先後做了六次檢測，其中五次均呈陰性反應。中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指，由於病毒已經入侵下呼吸道，所以在上呼吸道檢測均未能確診，他又認為暫時未有證據顯示，患者經空氣傳播而受感染。<br />\n<br />\n祿泉樓最新確診的33歲男患者在威爾斯親王醫院，他先後做了六次新冠病毒檢測，其中三次鼻咽拭子測試，以及深喉唾液樣本、糞便樣本檢測各一次，均對病毒呈陰性反應，直至周五進行支氣管鏡，深入患者發炎的左邊肺，抽取分泌物化驗，才確定感染新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394350&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=abd3d2ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394350&h=5ef594ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394350</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">專家來講，許樹昌似乎較可信</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"85e96f2c8203affe72e2db55b621a88a50ebb10b","tid":2063201,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇役症在於有冇遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}